      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "CHEQUES TO BURN (8) could manage only third at this track last time but impressed when clocking a dynamic 22.92 over 400m at this track the start prior. Hard to top on the time from two back. MAJOR QUEEN (7) hit the ground running from the squeeze draw with a strong early split last time, paving the way for a 2.25 lengths win at this track over 400m in 22.89. Ran one of the fastest times on the program in her latest win. Has hit winning form and can measure up again. ROCKLEA EARLE (2) returned a better run last time, finishing in the money (23.05) at this track behind MAJOR QUEEN in a Grade 5. Has the pace to be prominent. Recorded one of the quickest times on the card last start despite being beaten. Expected to feature again. HIGH CUBE (5) is a last start winner and can go on with it.",
